<h3 id="toc25"><span><a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/the-world-of-elrich">Elrich</a></span></h3>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wanderers-library.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/the-world-of-elrich/Elrich/medium.jpg" style="display: block; border: solid 1px #666; box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.25); width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p>The Kingdom of Elrich is the most ancient of all realms found upon the fair isle Elra. 'Tis a silly place, where elevators were invented before stairs, mystical marsupials are a grave threat to the monarchy's integrity, and cabbages have the final say in all matters.</p>
<p>Other kingdoms exist with them, realms such as the Union of the Four Empires, where squabbling co-monarchs have cause their entire realm to be cursed due to grocery-bagging ghost scandals. Gamenia focuses more on baked goods, and is a place where any croissant can find love. Suvians are renown for their prowess in war, but also have a thriving market for antiques. Those residing on the floating island of Cayle enjoy pineapple heads. Dolton has seen better days.</p>
<p>All of this and more can be explored in the realm of Elrich, more information on it can be found <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/the-world-of-elrich">in this magical glowing text</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
